    <div id="root"><div style="min-height: 100vh; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(15, 12, 41), rgb(48, 43, 99), rgb(36, 36, 62)); color: white; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, sans-serif;"><div style="text-align: center; padding: 48px 24px 24px;"><div style="font-size: 48px;">🔍</div><h1 style="font-size: 36px; margin: 8px 0px 0px; white-space: nowrap; padding-bottom: 8px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(167, 139, 250), rgb(96, 165, 250)) text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;">DataLens</h1><p style="color: rgb(160, 174, 192); font-size: 18px; margin-top: 8px;">Upload messy data. Get instant AI insights. Ask anything.</p></div><div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px 24px;"><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border: 2px dashed rgba(167, 139, 250, 0.4); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; text-align: center;"><p style="color: rgb(160, 174, 192); margin-bottom: 16px;">📂 Drop your CSV file here</p><input accept=".csv" type="file" style="color: white;"><p style="color: rgb(167, 139, 250); margin-top: 8px;">✓ movies.csv</p><button fdprocessedid="stek5y" style="margin-top: 16px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(124, 58, 237), rgb(37, 99, 235)); color: white; padding: 12px 32px; border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; opacity: 1;">✨ Analyze</button></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 24px; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; text-align: center;"><div><p style="color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px;">4,803</p><p style="color: rgb(160, 174, 192); margin: 0px;">Rows</p></div><div><p style="color: rgb(96, 165, 250); font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px;">24</p><p style="color: rgb(160, 174, 192); margin: 0px;">Columns</p></div><div><p style="color: rgb(52, 211, 153); font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0px;">6</p><p style="color: rgb(160, 174, 192); margin: 0px;">Insights</p></div></div><h2 style="color: white; margin-top: 32px;">💡 AI Insights</h2><div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px;"><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">📈 trend</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">The highest budget movie is Avatar with a budget of $237,000,000.</p></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">⚠️ anomaly</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">The longest movie is Avengers: Age of Ultron with a runtime of 141 minutes.</p></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">🔍 pattern</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">Most movies are produced in the United States, with 7 out of 10 movies produced in the US.</p></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">🔍 pattern</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">The most common genre is Action, with 7 out of 10 movies classified as Action.</p></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">📈 trend</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">The highest rated movie is The Dark Knight Rises with a rating of 7.6.</p></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07); border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(124, 58, 237);"><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 139, 250); font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;">🔍 pattern</span><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; color: rgb(226, 232, 240); line-height: 1.5;">The movies with the highest revenue are all superhero or action movies, indicating a pattern of high-revenue movies in these genres.</p></div></div><div style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; margin-top: 24px;"><h2 style="color: white; margin-top: 0px;">📊 Data Preview</h2><div class="recharts-responsive-container" style="width: 100%; height: 300px; min-width: 0px;"><div style="width: 0px; overflow-x: visible;"><div width="652" height="300" class="recharts-wrapper" style="position: relative; cursor: default; width: 652px; height: 300px;"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" tabindex="-1" class="recharts-tooltip-wrapper recharts-tooltip-wrapper-right recharts-tooltip-wrapper-top" style="visibility: hidden; pointer-events: none; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; transform: translate(249.6px, 229px);"><div class="recharts-default-tooltip" role="status" aria-live="assertive" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; background: rgb(26, 26, 46); border-width: medium; border-style: none; border-color: currentcolor; border-image: initial; white-space: nowrap; color: white;"><p class="recharts-tooltip-label" style="margin: 0px;"></p></div></div><svg role="application" tabindex="0" class="recharts-surface" width="652" height="300" viewBox="0 0 652 300" style="width: 100%; height: 10